quote><br />\n<br />\n靜同分手係無分別"},{"pid":"151487347c15e1900cdaf7f47018e7d69a940973","tid":247574,"uid":20882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"其實分手後由情侶關係變做陌生人 朋友 或者sp 邊種關係悲哀啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0888002daadf9370057d9536202de5cdc1c7f631","tid":247574,"uid":25452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實分手後由情侶關係變做陌生人 朋友 或者sp 邊種關係悲哀啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsp呢個直接拜拜<br />\n陌生人會對d 如果唔係和平分手<br />\n係和平分手嘅幾年後 大家擺低曬 可能仲做到朋友嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775d3da09b34248a8c444682fa716ecc7c5e2d15","tid":247574,"uid":32481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 主動溝另一個女仔 好快冇事"},{"pid":"18ed53f5b7c51c6981258f5fc3c591e1fcca9d52","tid":247574,"uid":25452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油 主動溝另一個女仔 好快冇事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望係咁啦<br />\n但又要擺低左先會去馬追第二個<br />\n如果唔係對第二個都唔公平<br />\n唉 睇幾時唔再掛住佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489f2bde67a56782aa0ee7e72479ece5604f85cf","tid":247574,"uid":67928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪分手呢樣野會傳染<br />\n我見感情台好多都話要冷靜下就分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前上黎都唔覺咁多呢啲post 一分左手呢幾日睇成個台都係分開下冷靜下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb92170a7839c3e4a6003705c87bba32ad0e120","tid":247574,"uid":67928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我ex話冷靜期 講好左某個時限俾個答案我<br />\n最後佢當撚左冷靜期=分手 問佢答案都唔撚應 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都當左冷靜=分手 所以無再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa44e312e1cb3736fd33b6fe8a0070b55f6c97f1","tid":247574,"uid":25452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我ex話冷靜期 講好左某個時限俾個答案我<br />\n最後佢當撚左冷靜期=分手 問佢答案都唔撚應 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都當左冷靜=分手 所以無再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抱住呢個心態都幾好<br />\n到佢真係講分手嘅時候<br />\n你都有曬準備 <br />\n可能心情仲會冇依家拖拖拉拉咁差<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8b55e4e6e35fe1ba7a5a37f38994ddd64cef3e","tid":247574,"uid":32481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打加油 主動溝另一個女仔 好快冇事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望係咁啦<br />\n但又要擺低左先會去馬追第二個<br />\n如果唔係對第二個都唔公平<br />\n唉 睇幾時唔再掛住佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未必 當你對另一個有feel 你就知自己以前係幾on9不㫁比假希望自己同埋你ed習慣黎 未必好似自己講到咁鐘意"},{"pid":"bdd20ac3d8aeed76b5ac4fad372a4c0ed8a2766f","tid":247574,"uid":67928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我ex話冷靜期 講好左某個時限俾個答案我<br />\n最後佢當撚左冷靜期=分手 問佢答案都唔撚應 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都當左冷靜=分手 所以無再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抱住呢個心態都幾好<br />\n到佢真係講分手嘅時候<br />\n你都有曬準備 <br />\n可能心情仲會冇依家拖拖拉拉咁差<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我都係好想搵佢 問埋最後一句<br />\n你冷靜完未 我地重新黎過好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都知道答案架啦 我預左接受到先去問<br />\n利申仲未敢問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239c94a2602